data.description: Centrally located sought after 4 bedroom 3 bath pool home!  Close to shopping, colleges, restaurants & entertainment!  Minutes to I 4 and I 95.  Welcoming front porch!  Family, living, dining and Florida rooms!  (Florida room is not counted in the living sq footage) GRAND primary suite with bath en-suite that includes double sinks, spacious garden tub and separate shower! Generous use of tile! Updated kitchen cabinetry and appliances! Natural gas heat, water heater, stove!  There is a separate hot water heater for primary bedroom section of house!   Could BE SOLD fully furnished!  BRAND NEW ROOF in Feb 2023. Heating & Cooling is 4 years old. Hurricane shutters on all windows! Electric screen on garage door. Sprinkler system and water softner!
